<text><body>
<cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">觀音菴</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址伍畆</cb:mulu>
<milestone unit="juan" n="7"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0158b11"/><cb:mulu type="卷" n="7"></cb:mulu><cb:juan fun="open" n="7"><cb:jhead>金陵梵剎志卷七</cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="B" n="0158b12"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">觀音閣</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">中剎</note>觀音閣　<note place="inline">勅建</note></head>
<lb ed="B" n="0158b13"/><p xml:id="pB29p0158b1301" style="margin-left:1em">在都城外即所綂靈谷寺下院東去寺伍里西去朝陽
<lb ed="B" n="0158b14"/>門叄里　太宗文皇帝嘗顧瞻山麓有氣不散命工琢
<lb ed="B" n="0158b15"/>石肖形搆閣以記其處正德庚午燬越伍年募緣重建
<lb ed="B" n="0158b16"/>中石壁光瑩如鏡所領小剎曰苜蓿菴</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0158b17"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">金剛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0158b1703" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">金剛殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">觀音殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0158b1708" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">觀音殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">左碑亭</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0158b1713" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">左碑亭<note place="inline">壹座</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">右碑亭</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0158b1718" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">右碑亭<note place="inline">壹座</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">正佛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0158b1723" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">正佛殿
<lb ed="B" n="0158b18"/><note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">毘盧殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0158b1803" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">毘盧殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">後捲蓬</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0158b1808" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">後捲蓬<note place="inline">壹楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">官房</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0158b1813" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">官房<note place="inline">貳拾楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0158b1818" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">拾房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址壹百貳拾玖丈</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0158b1822" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基址壹百
<lb ed="B" n="0158b19"/>貳拾玖丈<note place="inline">東至<g ref="#CB30220"/>家火巷　南至官街　西至王家火巷　北至民房</note></p></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0158b20"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">文</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">【文】</note></head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">重修觀音閣記略</cb:mulu><head>重修觀音閣記略</head><byline cb:type="author">明南兵部尚書太原喬宇</byline>
<pb ed="B" xml:id="B29.0160.0159a" n="0159a"/>
<lb ed="B" n="0159a01"/><p xml:id="pB29p0159a0101">南都第一山曰鍾山<g ref="#CB11694"/>江南北諸山及江漢諸水以獨鍾
<lb ed="B" n="0159a02"/>其秀望之者時若祥雲紫氣擁護旋繞我　太祖高皇帝
<lb ed="B" n="0159a03"/>陵廟在焉陵之東南有閣曰觀音閣正德庚午春罹欝攸
<lb ed="B" n="0159a04"/>之變太監蕭公通圖嗣興之越五年甲<note n="0159a0401" resp="CBETA" type="add">戌【CB】，戍【補編】</note><app n="0159a0401"><lem wit="【CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">戌</lem><rdg wit="【補編】">戍</rdg></app>始克就緒又明
<lb ed="B" n="0159a05"/>年而閣成蕭公詣余言曰公知兹閣之始乎我　太宗文
<lb ed="B" n="0159a06"/>皇帝纘承大綂綏靖四方追惟　聖祖肇建丕基祗謁
<lb ed="B" n="0159a07"/>　陵廟實興永慕顧瞻山麓有氣輪菌芬郁良久不散異之
<lb ed="B" n="0159a08"/>命工硺石肖形搆閣以紀其處召方外之有戒行者特虔
<lb ed="B" n="0159a09"/>焚修以仰荅　聖祖在天之靈意天人之格可以誠通而
<lb ed="B" n="0159a10"/>橋山劒舄之所瑞應禎祥之集又感通之所必有者所以
<lb ed="B" n="0159a11"/>祝鴻釐延景福匪徒為象教設也方閣之災公謀之諸同
<lb ed="B" n="0159a12"/>官所助金總千有餘兩筮日授事厥既經營庶工翕聚殿
<lb ed="B" n="0159a13"/>堂門廡煥焉一新都人士來觀妥靈有舍祈休有所棲僧
<lb ed="B" n="0159a14"/>有廬莫不忻然以喜如履樂界臨淨土而心目為之豁如
<lb ed="B" n="0159a15"/>也　正德十六年辛巳</p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
<lb ed="B" n="0159a16"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="1">苜蓿菴</cb:mulu><head><note place="inline">小剎</note>苜蓿菴</head>
<lb ed="B" n="0159a17"/><p xml:id="pB29p0159a1701" style="margin-left:1em">在都城外東城留守衛地洪武時建東去所領觀音閣
<lb ed="B" n="0159a18"/>二里西去朝陽門一里</p>
<lb ed="B" n="0159a19"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="2">殿堂</cb:mulu><head>【殿堂】</head><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">伽藍堂</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0159a1903" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">伽藍堂<note place="inline">壹楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">觀音殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0159a1908" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">觀音殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">正佛殿</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0159a1913" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">正佛殿<note place="inline">叄楹</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">僧院</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0159a1918" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">僧院<note place="inline">壹房</note></p></cb:div><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu type="其他" level="3">基址貳畆</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pB29p0159a1922" style="margin-left:2em" cb:place="inline">基址貳畆
<lb ed="B" n="0159a20"/><note place="inline">東至官路　南至官路　西至水溝　北至民園</note></p></cb:div></cb:div></cb:div>
</body></text></TEI>